Package: turbulencerealm-sindy
Version: 2.2.0
Section: science
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libegl1, libgl1, libglib2.0-0
Maintainer: Fayaz Rasheed <https://www.turbulencerealm.com>
Description: Turbulence Realm — SINDy
 Video-based fluid-flow analysis with Sparse Identification
 of Nonlinear Dynamics. Extracts velocity fields from video
 using optical flow, fits SINDy models, and provides rich
 visualisation, analysis, and export.
 .
 Features:
  * Optical flow (Farneback, Lucas-Kanade, TV-L1, RAFT)
  * SINDy modeling (polynomial, Fourier, combined libraries)
  * Analysis (vorticity, POD, DMD, spectra, turbulence stats)
  * Machine learning (PINN, FNO, DeepONet, ConvLSTM, VAE, GAN)
  * Export (CSV, HDF5, NetCDF, Parquet, PDF, MP4)
